Hungary forint ends up vs dlr , steady vs basket . Hungary ' s forint ended a little firmer against the dollar in quiet trade and steady against the central bank ' s currency basket , dealers said . The forint finished at 188 . 14 / 19 to the dollar , compared to 188 . 25 / 30 at opening . Zoltan Kalman of Hypo - Bank Hungaria said the market followed dollar / mark crosses . ( The forint floats within the NBH ' s 4 . 5 percent intervention range , against a currency basket made up 30 percent of the dollar and 70 percent of the mark . ) - - Budapest newsroom + 36 1 327 4040 
